    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As much as you might care for them, you've come to terms with the ephemeral nature of non-faerefolk, and it makes their threats feel less troublesome.</p><p>If a non-faerefolk rolls a failure on a check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.tHCqgwjtQtzNqVvd]{Coerce} you using Intimidation, it gets a critical failure instead (and thus can't try to Coerce you again for 1 week).</p><p>When a non-faerefolk attempts to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.2u915NdUyQan6uKF]{Demoralize} you, you become temporarily immune for 1 day, instead of 10 minutes.</p>",
